(Sign of Cross)

In nomine Patris, et Filii, et Spiritus Sancti. Amen
(In the name of the Father, and of the Son, and of the Holy Spirit. Amen. )

Per signum crucis de inimicis nostris libera nos, Deus noster. In nomine
Patris, et Filii, et Spiritus Sancti. Amen 
(By the sign of the cross deliver us from our enemies, Thou who art our
God. In the name of the Father, and of the Son, and of the Holy Spirit.
Amen.)
